Changes from the original:
  - Removed all TaskMaster integration (detection, init, parse, expand).
  - Removed autonomous task execution, time tracking, rollback, progress
    logging, and crash-recovery state.
  - Reduced `script.py` to three commands: load-template, validate-prd, backup-prd.
  - Re-labeled the four "taskmaster" validation checks as general "quality" checks.
  - De-branded the PRD templates.

